B. \left(x+\frac{1}{3}\right)^2-\frac{2}{9}
C. \left(x+\frac{1}{3}\right)^2-\frac{10}{9}
D. \left(x+\frac{1}{3}\right)^2-\frac{6}{9}
E. \left(x+\frac{1}{3}\right)^2-\frac{1}{3}
F. \left(x+\frac{1}{3}\right)^2-\frac{5}{9}
G. \left(x+\frac{1}{3}\right)^2-\frac{3}{9}
